3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper presents an automated liver segmentation framework, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MS (Medical Imaging): The paper focuses on liver segmentation using medical imaging data, which is a subfield of medical imaging. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with 3D liver segmentation using image information, which can be considered as a multimedia application.
